<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
It is a small level with small rooms surrounded by forest. It contains, as you might expect, only spider-type monsters, the worst of which are Elder Arenaes. They are quite tough and they can summon a lot of Arenaes which can cause critical wounds. Being surrounded can be quite dangerous. Bring lots of healing potions and use them freely (&gt;300 hps can be lost in one turn). <p>
Aside from the healing potions, you absolutely need to be poison resistant. Being stealthy is of great advantage since all arenaes tend to overlook intruders and an extra round of attacks can make all the difference. 
</p>
<p>
Once you have killed all the spiders you can get your reward from Celeborn. It is a potion of augmentation which increases all your stats. 
</p>
</div><div id="footer">


